{"tid":1059291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"裸上身自拍相做證  許廷鏗希雲街通宵會女友？","createTime":"2019-03-13T04:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T07:40:24.000Z","uid":61688,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1d18337b3b726da241085514990316ebb2173cd8","tid":1059291,"uid":61688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYhdWfH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYhdWfH.png&h=139ad352&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HV2mkHo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHV2mkHo.png&h=d5782286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n許廷鏗（Alfred）09年參加歌唱比賽入行，之後一邊做牙醫，一邊發展歌唱事業，今年是他入行第10年，早前更宣佈3月會在紅館舉行演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n由於Alfred屬唱得之人，故多年來獲不少前輩讚賞，亦有不少歌迷愛戴，但他甚少與異性傳緋聞，相反經常出現「斷背」疑雲，和胡鴻鈞亦曾經傳緋聞，惟兩人對緋聞均一笑置之，胡鴻鈞更講笑說他們出雙入對多年。<br />\n<br />\nAlfred早前在演唱會記招被女模狂咀後，亦自爆dry了很久沒有拍拖，不過近日有讀者楊先生向《蘋果》爆料，指Alfred頻頻約人在銅鑼灣希雲街密會。<br />\n<br />\n前年Alfred在歌曲《神奇之旅》填上幾句歌詞「我信一天會遇上極光，為求環抱星與夢竭力前望，路過希雲街當它冰島札幌」，之後說過詞中這3個地方 對他有微妙意思，想不到今次被指密會的地方，剛巧又在希雲街，而據知他在那裏有一個和胞兄持有的物業單位。<br />\n<br />\n讀者楊先生報料指，其好友向他表示，身邊有朋友正跟Alfred秘密來往，除了在農曆新年到訪Alfred位於大圍寓所，由凌晨3時至早上9時多一直單獨相處，之後再有相約去銅鑼灣希雲街見面，同樣過了一整晚才離開。<br />\n<br />\n楊先生坦言，一班朋友本來都有懷疑，但3月2日，楊先生朋友的友人又約了Alfred，大家於是齊齊在希雲街守候，結果在晚上接近10時，果真見到Alfred出現，他急急腳走上了一座唐樓，友人更把朋友分享給他的「福利圖」發送給大家看，包括兩張Alfred對着鏡的自拍照，其中一張Alfred更是赤裸上身，露出白滑肚皮。不過，<span style=\"color: red;\">楊先生報料時表示友人未有透露相約Alfred的朋友是男是女</span>，表示要保障朋友，只估計Alfred相約的是女性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190313/59361955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F59361955&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=b1c738a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F59361955&h=dc641ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190313/59361955</a>"},{"pid":"d9bd949f3034dd9e5143667b28a09c8f23ed4571","tid":1059291,"uid":61688,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"好想同佢瘋狂做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a741012a46dc9ff244f3542e2f5f75b4c17927aa","tid":1059291,"uid":112089,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"我希望唔係TL"},{"pid":"aa72658c7b7adf6d7d49104b0561c382362683f5","tid":1059291,"uid":34777,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:41:38.000Z","msg":"個友人都幾仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146f0b743254e1f5d08c9518aaae4a33f6dd6eef","tid":1059291,"uid":3189,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"裸上身約gay佬激戰？"},{"pid":"da7b133649f5f4c76a4840a60c1ad76f996e654d","tid":1059291,"uid":15274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"鏗鏗真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc595802bcd983daf42978a1bc87cbcb617037c0","tid":1059291,"uid":61688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"146f0b743254e1f5d08c9518aaae4a33f6dd6eef","tid":1059291,"uid":3189,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"裸上身約gay佬激戰？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"好明顯係搵fun<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d825203c8ba68d6928cd060313ccffcbb8a98291","tid":1059291,"uid":3189,"like":2,